1.1 Batch Size¶

In [9]:
parameter_name = 'batch'
In [10]:
overall_avg_lifetime = []
overall_cost = []
overall_computational_time = []

parameter_range = [10, 50, 100, 500]

for batch in parameter_range:

    n_iter = total_games / batch
    grid_size = 10
    simulation = BioCells(random_corner_init=True)
    n_input = grid_size**2
    model = FullyConnected(n_input=n_input, n_hidden=200, n_classes=4)

    start_time = time.time()
    avg_lifetime, avg_reward, computation_time = train(model, simulation,
                                                       batch_size=batch,
                                                       n_iterations=int(n_iter),
                                                       gamma=0.7,
                                                       learning_rate=0.01,
                                                       grid_size=10,
                                                       tree_search=False,
                                                       ts_prop=0.5)

    end_time = time.time()

    overall_avg_lifetime.append(avg_lifetime)
    overall_cost.append(avg_reward)
    overall_computational_time.append(computation_time)

print('Done...')

    grid_size = 10
    simulation = BioCells(random_corner_init=True)
    n_input = grid_size**2
    model = FullyConnected(n_input=n_input, n_hidden=200, n_classes=4)

    start_time = time.time()
    avg_lifetime, avg_reward, computation_time = train(model, simulation,
                                                       batch_size=batch_size,
                                                       n_iterations=int(n_iter),

                                                       grid_size=10,
                                                       tree_search=False,

    end_time = time.time()

    overall_avg_lifetime.append(avg_lifetime)

    grid_size = 10
    simulation = BioCells(random_corner_init=True)
    n_input = grid_size**2
    model = FullyConnected(n_input=n_input, n_hidden=200, n_classes=4)

    start_time = time.time()

                                                       batch_size=batch_size,
                                                       n_iterations=int(n_iter),
                                                       gamma=0.8,
                                                       learning_rate=parameter,
                                                       grid_size=10,
                                                       tree_search=False,
                                                       ts_prop=0.5)

    end_time = time.time()

    overall_avg_lifetime.append(avg_lifetime)
    overall_cost.append(avg_reward)
    overall_computational_time.append(computation_time)

print('Done...')

overall_avg_lifetime = []
overall_cost = []
overall_computational_time = []

parameter_range = [0, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8]

batch_size = 128
n_iter = int(total_games/batch_size)

for parameter in parameter_range:
    
    grid_size = 10
    simulation = BioCells(random_corner_init=True)
    n_input = grid_size**2
    model = FullyConnected(n_input=n_input, n_hidden=200, n_classes=4)

    start_time = time.time()
    avg_lifetime, avg_reward, computation_time = train(model, simulation,
                                                       batch_size=batch_size,
                                                       n_iterations=int(n_iter),
                                                       gamma=0.8,
                                                       learning_rate=0.1,
                                                       grid_size=10,
                                                       tree_search=True,
                                                       ts_prop=parameter)

    end_time = time.time()

    overall_avg_lifetime.append(avg_lifetime)
    overall_cost.append(avg_reward)
    overall_computational_time.append(computation_time)

print('Done...')

1.6 Tree Search:¶












In [79]:



    


parameter_name = 'Tree Search Multiple Runs'

















In [81]:



    


total_games = 5000

















In [82]:



    


overall_avg_lifetime = []
overall_cost = []
overall_computational_time = []

parameter_range = [0, 0.2, 0.4]

batch_size = 128
n_iter = int(total_games/batch_size)

for parameter in parameter_range:
    
    distributions = np.empty((0, n_iter))
    
    for repeat in range(4):
    
        grid_size = 10
        simulation = BioCells(random_corner_init=True)
        n_input = grid_size**2
        model = FullyConnected(n_input=n_input, n_hidden=200, n_classes=4)

        start_time = time.time()
        avg_lifetime, avg_reward, computation_time = train(model, simulation,
                                                           batch_size=batch_size,
                                                           n_iterations=int(n_iter),
                                                           gamma=0.9,
                                                           learning_rate=0.001,
                                                           grid_size=10,
                                                           tree_search=True,
                                                           ts_prop=parameter)
        
        distributions = np.vstack((distributions, avg_lifetime))
    
    overall_avg_lifetime.append(distributions)

print('Done...')
